<p><b>John Fante</b> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1909-04-08"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="04-08"><a href="/wiki/April_8" title="April 8">April 8</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1909" title="1909">1909</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1983-05-08"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="05-08"><a href="/wiki/May_8" title="May 8">May 8</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1983" title="1983">1983</a></span>) was an <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a> novelist, short story writer and screenwriter of Italian descent.</p>
